sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Browser
    participant SPA
    participant Backend
    participant Database

    User->>Browser: 1. Navigate to SPA
    Browser->>SPA: 2. Load HTML/CSS/JS
    SPA->>SPA: 3. Initialize SPA frontend

    SPA->>Backend: 4. GET /api/notes
    Backend->>Database: 5. Query database
    Database-->>Backend: 6. Return notes JSON
    Backend-->>SPA: 7. Return data to SPA

    SPA->>Browser: 8. Render notes dynamically

    Note right of User: User interacts with SPA
    User->>SPA: Add/Delete/Update note
    SPA->>Backend: POST/PUT/DELETE note
    Backend->>Database: Update DB
    Database-->>Backend: Confirmation
    Backend-->>SPA: Updated note data
    SPA->>Browser: Update UI dynamically
